itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 1/31/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are in the studio talking about the tragic death of Cheslie Kryst, Valentine's Day, and the Super Bowl. Callers share a little too much information about their hustles and scams. 

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
